    "recap_headline": "Stephen F. Austin",
    "recap_text": "HAMMOND, La. -\nStephen F. Austin was limited to just three hits in Friday night's Southland Conference opener at Southeastern Louisiana and the host Lions took a 3-0 lead through two innings of play en route to an 8-1 win from\u00a0Pat Kenelly Diamond at Alumni Field. The loss drops SFA to 11-8 overall with a 4-3 record in SLC action. SLU improves to 10-8 and 3-1 in conference play.\nJhett Creel\n,\nJulian Swift\nand\nEthan Adkisson\naccounted for SFA's hits in the loss with Swift doubling in the ninth.\nCooper Schneider\ngrounded out in the eighth to plate Adkisson for the Jacks' lone run. Adkisson tripled to lead off the eighth inning prior to Schneider's at bat.\nOn the mound,\nGabe LeBlanc\nwent 4.0 innings with the Lions plating five runs on ten hits during his outing.\nBrennan Greer\nand\nCharlie Feris\ncombined on the final four innings with two apiece.\nPOSTGAME NOTES\nTwo of SFA's three hits went for extra bases pushing the team's 2026 total to 53\nAdkisson's triple was the fifth by a Jack this season and he is the fourth to register a three-bagger\nLeBlanc fanned four to run his season total in strikeouts to 14\nThe Jacks struck out a season-high 11 times on Friday\nSFA stranded ten SLU base runners and walked just four Lions\nSECURE YOUR SEATS TODAY\nSingle game tickets\nfor all SFA baseball home games are available now. Fans interested in purchasing season ticket packages can secure their seats\nhere\n. Don't miss out on all the exciting action from Pilgrim's Park this season!\nTHE JACKS HAVE GONE MOBILE\nSFA Athletics' newest mobile phone application is designed to bring Lumberjack fans closer to the action than ever before. Available now on both the App Store and Google Play, the new SFA Athletics app delivers schedules, scores, rosters, news, ticket access, and exclusive content right to your phone. Fans can also receive push notifications, so they never miss a moment of the action. Download now:\nOfficial SFA Athletics App\n.\nFOLLOW THE JACKS\nFor all the latest information on SFA baseball, visit\nSFAjacks.com\n. For up-to-the-minute updates, follow the\u00a0Jacks\u00a0on\nX\n,\nInstagram\nand\nFacebook\n.\n#LogByLog"
